Aging and vascular dysfunction: beneficial melatonin effects.

Rodella LF(1), Favero G, Rossini C, Foglio E, Bonomini F, Reiter RJ, Rezzani R.

Author information:
(1)Department of Biomedical Sciences and Biotechnologies, Section of Human 
Anatomy, University of Brescia, Viale Europa 11, Brescia, Italy.

